---
<section class="benefits-section">
  <div class="container container-sm">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2>Here's What You'll Learn Inside</h2>
      <p class="section-desc">The precise roadmap to energetic sovereignty.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="benefits-list">
      
      <div class="benefit-item glass-panel">
        <div class="icon">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="color: #fff"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3>The Baseline Shield</h3>
          <p>Learn the 3-minute morning routine that seals your aura from parasitic attachments before you even leave the house.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="benefit-item glass-panel">
        <div class="icon">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="color: #fff"><circle cx="6" cy="6" r="3"/><circle cx="6" cy="18" r="3"/><line x1="20" y1="4" x2="8.12" y2="15.88"/><line x1="14.47" y1="14.48" x2="20" y2="20"/><line x1="8.12" y1="8.12" x2="12" y2="12"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3>Severing Unwanted Cords</h3>
          <p>Discover the exact visualization and physical grounding techniques to permanently cut ties with toxic individuals or entities.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="benefit-item glass-panel">
        <div class="icon">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="color: #fff"><path d="M1 12s4-8 11-8 11 8 11 8-4 8-11 8-11-8-11-8z"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3>Identifying the Infiltrators</h3>
          <p>How to tell the difference between your own natural anxiety and a psychic attack from an external source.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="benefit-item glass-panel">
        <div class="icon">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="color: #fff"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/><polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3>Fortifying Your Space</h3>
          <p>Simple, actionable steps to clear your home or bedroom of lingering dark energies so you can finally sleep in peace.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .benefits-section {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    position: relative;
  }

  .container-sm {
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-desc {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .benefits-list {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .benefit-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    transition: transform var(--transition-fast), border-color var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .benefit-item:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    border-color: var(--primary);
  }

  .icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2);
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 12px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  h3 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: #e2e8f0;
  }

  p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .benefits-list { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .benefits-section { padding: 4rem 0; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .benefit-item { flex-direction: column; gap: 1.25rem; padding: 1.5rem; }
    .benefit-item:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); }
    .icon { width: 50px; height: 50px; font-size: 2rem; }
    h3 { font-size: 1.2rem; }
  }
</style>
